com.hedera.hashgraph.sdk.token

Class TokenUpdateTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hedera.hashgraph.sdk.HederaCall<com.hedera.hashgraph.proto.Transaction,com.hedera.hashgraph.proto.TransactionResponse,Resp,T>
      • com.hedera.hashgraph.sdk.TransactionBuilder<TransactionId,Transaction,T>
        • com.hedera.hashgraph.sdk.SingleTransactionBuilder<TokenUpdateTransaction>
          • com.hedera.hashgraph.sdk.token.TokenUpdateTransaction

  • public final class TokenUpdateTransaction
extends SingleTransactionBuilder<TokenUpdateTransaction>
    Updates an already created Token. If no value is given for a field, that field is left unchanged. For an immutable tokens (that is, a token created without an adminKey), only the expiry may be updated. Setting any other field in that case will cause the transaction status to resolve to TOKEN_IS_IMMUTABlE.
